      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 40 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 40 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：田獲三狐，得黃矢，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject catch, in hunting, three foxes, and obtain the yellow (= golden) arrows. With firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
