      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 40 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 40 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：解而拇，朋至斯孚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(To the subject of) the fourth NINE, undivided, (it is said), 'Remove your toes. Friends will (then) come, between you and whom there will be mutual confidence.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
