      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 40 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：公用射隼，于高墉之上，獲之，无不利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the sixth SIX, divided, we see a feudal prince (with his bow) shooting at a falcon on the top of a high wall, and hitting it. (The effect of his action) will be in every way advantageous.</seg>
      </tuv>
